SELECT DISTINCT
	"SysSchema"."Name",
	"SysEntitySchemaReference"."ColumnName"
FROM
	"public"."SysEntitySchemaReference"
	INNER JOIN "public"."SysSchema" ON ("SysSchema"."Id" = "SysEntitySchemaReference"."SysSchemaId")
WHERE
	"SysEntitySchemaReference"."ReferenceSchemaId" = @P1
	AND NOT "SysEntitySchemaReference"."ColumnName" IN (@P2, @P3)
SELECT * FROM public."tsp_GetSysSchemaParentsInPackageHierarchy"(@StartSchemaUId, @WorkspaceId)

WITH RECURSIVE
	"HierarchicalSelect" AS (
SELECT
	"ParentSchema"."Id" "IdAutoAlias",
	"ParentSchema"."Name" "NameAutoAlias",
	"ParentSchema"."ParentId" "ParentIdAutoAlias",
	0 "Level"
FROM
	"public"."SysSchema" "ParentSchema"
	INNER JOIN "public"."SysPackage" "WorkspacePackage" ON ("WorkspacePackage"."Id" = "ParentSchema"."SysPackageId"
	AND "WorkspacePackage"."SysWorkspaceId" = @WorkspaceId)
WHERE
	"ParentSchema"."ExtendParent" = @ExtendParent
	AND "ParentSchema"."Id" IN (
SELECT
	"StartingSchema"."Id"
FROM
	"public"."SysSchema" "StartingSchema"
	INNER JOIN "public"."SysPackage" "StartingPackage" ON ("StartingPackage"."Id" = "StartingSchema"."SysPackageId"
	AND "StartingPackage"."SysWorkspaceId" = @WorkspaceId)
WHERE
	"StartingSchema"."Name" = (
SELECT
	"SearchSchema"."Name"
FROM
	"public"."SysSchema" "SearchSchema"
WHERE
	"SearchSchema"."UId" = @SchemaUId
LIMIT 1)
	AND "StartingSchema"."ExtendParent" = @ExtendParent)
UNION ALL
SELECT
	"ParentSchema"."Id" "Id",
	"ParentSchema"."Name" "Name",
	"ParentSchema"."ParentId" "ParentId",
	"Level" + 1
FROM
	"public"."SysSchema" "ParentSchema"
	INNER JOIN "public"."SysPackage" "WorkspacePackage" ON ("WorkspacePackage"."Id" = "ParentSchema"."SysPackageId"
	AND "WorkspacePackage"."SysWorkspaceId" = @WorkspaceId)
	INNER JOIN "HierarchicalSelect" ON ("HierarchicalSelect"."ParentIdAutoAlias" = "ParentSchema"."Id")
WHERE
	"ParentSchema"."ExtendParent" = @ExtendParent
)
SELECT
	"IdAutoAlias" "Id",
	"NameAutoAlias" "Name",
	"ParentIdAutoAlias" "ParentId"
FROM
	"HierarchicalSelect"

	"ResourceSelect"."PackageName" "PackageName",
	"ResourceSelect"."PackageId" "PackageId",

	"ResourceSelect"."ModifiedOn" "ModifiedOn",
	"ResourceSelect"."Key" "Key",
	"ResourceSelect"."Value" "Value",

	"ResourceSelect"."ImageData" "ImageData"
FROM
	(
SELECT
	"LocalizableValue"."SysSchemaId" "SchemaId",
	"SysSchema"."UId" "SchemaUId",
	"SysSchema"."Name" "SchemaName",
	"SysPackage"."Name" "PackageName",
	"LocalizableValue"."SysPackageId" "PackageId",
	"LocalizableValue"."SysCultureId" "CultureId",
	"LocalizableValue"."ModifiedOn" "ModifiedOn",
	"LocalizableValue"."Key" "Key",
	"LocalizableValue"."Value" "Value",
	"LocalizableValue"."ResourceType" "ResourceType",
	"LocalizableValue"."ImageData" "ImageData"

	"public"."SysLocalizableValue" "LocalizableValue"
	INNER JOIN "public"."SysPackage" ON ("SysPackage"."Id" = "LocalizableValue"."SysPackageId")
	INNER JOIN "public"."SysSchema" ON ("SysSchema"."Id" = "LocalizableValue"."SysSchemaId")
WHERE
	"SysPackage"."SysWorkspaceId" = @P1
	AND "LocalizableValue"."SysPackageId" IN (
SELECT
	"SysPackageId"
FROM
	"public"."SysSchema"
WHERE
	"Id" IN (@P2, @P3, @P4))
	AND "LocalizableValue"."SysSchemaId" IN (@P5, @P6, @P7)) "ResourceSelect"
	INNER JOIN (
SELECT
	"SysPackage"."Id" "SysPackageId",
	"SysPackage"."Position" "PackagePosition",
	(

	MAX("SysPackageHierarchy"."Level")
FROM
	"public"."SysPackageHierarchy"
WHERE
	"SysPackageHierarchy"."BaseSysPackageId" = "SysPackage"."Id") "PackageLevel"
FROM
	"public"."SysPackage") "PackagesWithMaxLevel" ON ("PackagesWithMaxLevel"."SysPackageId" = "ResourceSelect"."PackageId")

	"PackagesWithMaxLevel"."PackageLevel" DESC NULLS LAST,
	"PackagePosition" DESC NULLS LAST,
	"PackageName" ASC NULLS FIRST
